data.description: This stunning property offers the perfect blend of comfort, space, and potential income. Situated on a generous half-acre lot, this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a true gem.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting and spacious living area with exposed beams. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area and kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining friends and family.  The four bedrooms provide comfortable retreats, each offering generous space and storage options.  The true highlight of this property is the 400 sq ft potential income producing apartment. With its own private entry, kitchen, and bathroom, that offers endless possibilities. Whether you choose to rent it out for additional income, use it as a guest suite, or as a private retreat for a family member, the choice is yours.  Schedule your showing today!
